<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Open in Profile — Settings</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --navy: #1e3a5f; --blue: #2d6a9f; --green: #16a34a;
      --text: #1e293b; --muted: #64748b; --border: #e2e8f0; --bg: #f8fafc;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      max-width: 580px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 36px 24px 64px;
    }

    .top {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .top-icon {
      width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), var(--blue));
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 20px; color: #fff; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .top h1 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; }
    .top p  { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; }

    /* Info banner */
    .info-banner {
      background: #eff6ff;
      border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #1e40af;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .info-banner .icon { font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }

    /* Section */
    .section-label {
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .7px;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* Profile cards */
    #profileList { margin-bottom: 12px; }

    .pCard {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      transition: box-shadow 0.15s;
    }
    .pCard:hover { box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(30,58,95,0.07); }
    .pCard.new-profile { border-color: #bfdbfe; background: #eff6ff; }

    .avatar {
      width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #fff; flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .pCard-fields { flex: 1; display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; }

    .field-wrap { flex: 1; }
    .field-wrap label {
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .5px; color: #94a3b8; display: block; margin-bottom: 3px;
    }
    .field-wrap input {
      width: 100%; padding: 6px 10px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 7px;
      font-size: 13px; font-family: inherit; color: var(--text);
      background: var(--bg);
      transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
    }
    .field-wrap input:focus {
      outline: none; border-color: var(--blue);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(45,106,159,0.12);
      background: #fff;
    }
    .field-wrap input.dir-input {
      font-family: 'Menlo','Consolas',monospace; font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted);
    }

    .removeBtn {
      background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 18px; color: #cbd5e1; padding: 4px; border-radius: 6px;
      transition: color 0.15s, background 0.15s; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .removeBtn:hover { color: #dc2626; background: #fef2f2; }

    /* Detect button */
    .detect-row {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .detectBtn {
      background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 8px 16px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer;
      color: var(--navy); font-family: inherit; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
    }
    .detectBtn:hover { background: #eff6ff; border-color: var(--blue); color: var(--blue); }
    .detect-hint { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); }

    /* Actions */
    .actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; margin-top: 16px; }

    .addBtn {
      background: none; border: 1px dashed var(--border); border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 8px 16px; font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer; color: var(--blue);
      font-family: inherit;
    }
    .addBtn:hover { background: #eff6ff; border-color: var(--blue); }

    .saveBtn {
      background: var(--navy); color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 9px 22px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer;
      font-family: inherit; transition: background 0.15s;
    }
    .saveBtn:hover { background: var(--blue); }

    #saveStatus { font-size: 13px; color: var(--green); }

    /* Dir hint */
    .dir-hint {
      background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px 16px; margin-top: 24px; font-size: 12.5px; line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    .dir-hint strong { color: var(--text); }
    code {
      background: #f1f5f9; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 1px 6px; font-family: 'Menlo','Consolas',monospace; font-size: 11.5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="top">
  <div class="top-icon">⇄</div>
  <div>
    <h1>Profile Settings</h1>
    <p>Configure once — applies to all your Chrome profiles automatically.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="info-banner">
  <span class="icon">ℹ️</span>
  <span>Settings are stored on your computer, not per-profile. Rename a profile here and every Chrome window sees the change immediately. No need to set this up more than once.</span>
</div>

<div class="section-label">Your Chrome Profiles</div>

<div class="detect-row">
  <button class="detectBtn" id="detectBtn">🔍 Auto-detect my profiles</button>
  <span class="detect-hint">Finds all Chrome profiles on this PC</span>
</div>

<div id="profileList"></div>

<div class="actions">
  <button class="addBtn" id="addBtn">+ Add manually</button>
  <button class="saveBtn" id="saveBtn">Save</button>
  <span id="saveStatus"></span>
</div>

<div class="dir-hint">
  <strong>Finding a Profile Directory name manually:</strong><br />
  Open Chrome in that profile → go to <code>chrome://version</code> → look at <em>Profile Path</em>.<br />
  The last folder segment is the value to use — e.g. <code>Default</code>, <code>Profile 1</code>, <code>Profile 2</code>.
</div>

<script src="options.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
